CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 17, 1945, pg. 3 reads: "Pitt Director - Dr. Dorothy Rood, director of the Department of Public Health Nurses of the University of Pittsburgh, will be principal speaker at the Centre Avenue YMCA, Wednesday, Nov. 21, at the monthly health lecture series. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Dr. Dorothy Rood seated in upholstered chair at desk in office interior, another pose
